In SURFEX modi_... are generated during the compilation of the code. 
Here we converted subroutines to "modi_" module manually.

For example, subroutine SURFACE_RI.F90
converted to a module 
using this structure 

MODULE MODI_SURFACE_RI
CONTAINS
  SUBROUTINE MODI_SURFACE_RI_SUB(args)
  ...
  END SUBROUTINE MODI_SURFACE_RI_SUB
END MODULE MODI_SURFACE_RI
